            <h2 class="bg-clip">Thought leadership.</h2>
            <p>At Kruger Products, we recognize that we have valuable experience to share  and valuable knowledge to gain. With this in mind, we partnered with Canadian Grocer in 2012 and created our Leaders in Sustainable Thinking thought leadership roundtable series. Our goal: to uncover innovative solutions for consumer packaged goods manufacturers and retailers, and to promote industry best practices.</p>
